    "By doing so, the reader can get an understanding of the range of the study of the given problem and potential obstacles of the review process.",
    "Conclusion and future work Key findingsThis study demonstrates that the integration of AI in higher education offers significant opportunities for enhancing educational outcomes, operational efficiency, and sustainability.",
    "AI-powered personalized learning platforms improve student engagement and retention through tailored educational experiences, while predictive analytics provides timely interventions for at-risk students [96].",
    "Operationally, AI-driven systems for energy and waste management align financial savings with sustainability goals, reducing environmental impact [97].",
    "However, AI implementation in higher education is not without challenges."
